OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1772381499
OL,3,C'No plan B' for professional rugby in
OL,4,CWales, admits WRU chair
OL,6,FThe proposals to reduce the number of
OL,7,Fprofessional clubs were met with
OL,8,Fchallenge from Alun Davies, the MS for
OL,9,FBlaenau Gwent.
OL,11,FHe argued that cutting teams was an
OL,12,Fadmission of failure in growth, rather
OL,13,Fthan a strategy for success.
OL,15,F"Surely the alternative to what you're
OL,16,Fproposing isn't to reduce the number
OL,17,Fof people playing professional rugby,"
OL,18,FMr Davies said, "It is to actually
OL,19,Fgrow the game in Wales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
