PN,46706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1772381499
OL,3,C'No plan B' for professional rugby in
OL,4,CWales, admits WRU chair
OL,6,F"There are lots of children in Blaenau
OL,7,FGwent who want to play rugby, who want
OL,8,Fthe opportunity to go through that
OL,9,Fpyramid."
OL,11,FWhile Mr Collier-Keywood agreed that
OL,12,Fgrowth was a "key part" of the union's
OL,13,Fstrategy, he insisted the current
OL,14,Fmodel was financially impossible.
OL,16,F"The fact remains that we have four
OL,17,Fteams that don't have enough money to
OL,18,Fplay at the professional level that
OL,19,Fthey are being asked to play at," the
OL,20,Fchair replied.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
