PN,46707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1772381499
OL,3,C'No plan B' for professional rugby in
OL,4,CWales, admits WRU chair
OL,6,FHe added: "We don't have the finances
OL,7,Fto fund all four teams and to fund the
OL,8,Fnecessary rugby infrastructure within
OL,9,FWales to enable us to do exactly what
OL,10,Fyou're asking us to do there."
OL,12,FWith the 12 April deadline
OL,13,Fapproaching, the WRU board is expected
OL,14,Fto announce a formal date for the
OL,15,Fmeeting in the coming days.
OL,17,FIf the vote of no confidence passes,
OL,18,Fit will not only cast doubt on the
OL,19,F"Three-Region" plan but could trigger
OL,20,Fa total overhaul of the union's
OL,21,Fexecutive leadership.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/8
